efficiency: HIGH
time complexity: O(1)
space complexity: O(1)
energy implications: LOW
explanation: After 3 presses the 6 possible distinct states repeat every 2 presses, so only 8 unique states exist. Special-case handling for small n and presses gives the exact count without simulation.

